e,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不……你可以得诺贝尔数学奖。(手动狗头\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560044311,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0dc28834679eba40c6b827a4cd6088ee","url_token":"qin-shi-zun-98","name":"秦世尊","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0dc28834679eba40c6b827a4cd6088ee","user_type":"people","headline":"大学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560044311","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545804444,"updated_time":1545804444,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我也证明出来了歌德巴赫猜想，等一月一日我看看咱俩方法一不一样\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560676853,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4e2084aaf135ac92452c54bfc52a485a","url_token":"yu-qi-qi-64-30","name":"居居蓝","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6984f7b052d1a749417bf40eb642c749_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6984f7b052d1a749417bf40eb642c749_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4e2084aaf135ac92452c54bfc52a485a","user_type":"people","headline":"不胖到120斤不换签名","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560676853","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545878717,"updated_time":1545966723,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e手痒来答一发。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e短短几天，眼睁睁地看着吃瓜群众的数量从几十个变成了几W个……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b11444181781a29441692bba18041110_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b11444181781a29441692bba18041110_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-57540aab35ef46eba70c549816f3ff91_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e从现有的回答看，98%的人都持怀疑看法，表示从未见过逼乎下的回答态度如此一致。。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePS :  这个问题简直我的快乐源泉，工作学习累了就来看看最新回答，哈哈。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么这个问题为啥能激起大家的g点呢，\u003cb\u003e因为短短一句话的问题，有三个关键点，高中生，哥猜，清华保送。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e先说下哥猜。\u003c/b\u003e  本人文科数学渣，所以对数学知识的认识止步于高中。前几天才知乎刷到了这个问题，阅读一些数学大佬的回答后，对哥猜这个定理不明觉厉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e再说高中\u003c/b\u003e。。我们不妨来假设一下，如果提问者没有说自己证明了这个定理，只是以一个高中生对高等数学的好奇，和求学途径的一种可能在知乎发问，那么现在回答中冷嘲热讽的比例至少少一半。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么回答中有人会热心普及哥猜这个定理的证明难度，有人会欣赏年轻人初生牛犊不怕虎的样子像极了自己当年，鼓励他保持求知欲，继续学习研究……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但提问者信誓旦旦地说已经证毕，还自信地说没有任何漏洞，1月1日欢迎观看，这味道就不一样了。不啻在质疑数学界的权威性…\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有句话叫  无知者无畏，我觉得挺符合他现在这种情况的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e各种可能大家都说的很全面了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e现在我们总结下大致有这样几种观点：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e1.提问者是个只有初等数学程度的高中生。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学成绩和智商优于同学，但对哥猜知其然而不知所以然。所以“以为”自己已经证明出，想走捷径求学；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e2.提问者是个民科数学家。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e开了个昵称为“证明”的新号提问哥猜，且问题中故意带有高中生博眼球，涨粉张热度。也不排除有团队背后操作的可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e3.题主真的是天赋异禀，真的证明了这个定理…（当然这种可能不大）\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实我比较怀疑他这篇证明的文章怎么放上来…以这种证明过程难度，没有个几千张纸完不成吧，好害怕他扔个邮箱在这里…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613\" data-hash=\"a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613\"\u003e@Sun Ao\u003c/a\u003e   很真诚的回答。但到达的认知层面决定了看问题的高度和角度，他可能不能完全理解和接受你的想法。毕竟这盘棋已经铺的这么大，，1.1那天是一地鸡毛还是一鸣惊人，都会成为他人生浓墨重彩的一笔。希望提问者看到这个答案\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我们在这里拭目以待，因为不管他有没有证出，1月1号这天，这个提问都会上知乎首页的\u003c/b\u003e \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561365968,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4b51a540259dcb743e84231208353fed","url_token":"wang-yuan-13-52-38","name":"大总攻夜幕","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-839cfd3ed9080d1988306ba78830df18_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-839cfd3ed9080d1988306ba78830df18_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4b51a540259dcb743e84231208353fed","user_type":"people","headline":"无业人员","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561365968","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545962431,"updated_time":1545962651,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e身为一个物理人士没有什么过多的评论可言。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是听说题主，要发布证明的那位需要投稿。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我可以很明确的告诉你，你这样大牛级的工作就应该投在nature，science这样的期刊上。如果你的英语水平不够，我可以帮你，给我个三作就好，我甚至还可以帮你修改论文的学术规范要求。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许，你将会是第一个得到菲尔兹奖的本土中国人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样我也能吃个瓜青史留名。    \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不谢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e送我上去，让原po看到。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………切割线…………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e后续，另外我在清华数学也有几位认识的教授。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证明是真的，可以立刻帮你通知。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560248149,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a304cb9cc5e2df7e14b9b868e082753f","url_token":"xiao-ming-tong-xue-28-93","name":"小明同学","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b3ec27a46c7315ac2b2a05da65b3fe39_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b3ec27a46c7315ac2b2a05da65b3fe39_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a304cb9cc5e2df7e14b9b868e082753f","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560248149","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545822423,"updated_time":1545822423,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e无论你的证明是否成立，兄弟，我都佩服你，在这场事件中，最珍贵的莫过于你那敢于挑战的精神\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561504321,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6d097ecf988531814d448865697be3d","url_token":"luo-hua-sheng-23-46","name":"罗化生","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebb1c461788a19a1cb71e7e4c1bd7664_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebb1c461788a19a1cb71e7e4c1bd7664_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6d097ecf988531814d448865697be3d","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561504321","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545973437,"updated_time":1545974116,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主还是一个高中生，视野确实容易比较狭隘，说一下个人的经历以及个人证明哥德巴赫猜想的历程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当年还在读高中的时候，也觉得考上清华北大是无上的荣光，是追求的一个重大的目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但几年以后，随着心态的平和，对于考上什么大学，获得什么学位之类的根本不放在心上了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只要你有自己的研究成果，干嘛一定要有什么学位？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使暂时没有学术成果，自己自由自在的探索也够了，毕竟数学这个东西有一个好处就是不需要实验室，反过来说如果在某些研究院所里，各种禁锢的可能更多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里很多人对题主进行嘲讽，是中国教育缺乏最重要的一环：尊重教育的体现，不必在意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人研究过哥德巴赫猜想，我估计你的证明很可能存在一些逻辑上的不严谨。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是不管怎么样，敢于探索，敢于思考总是好事，你可能证明哥德巴赫猜想不成功，但是你最少锤炼了你的思维，这是有助于你以后的探索其他领域的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，也不要过分的陷进去，毕竟你追求的是数学，而不是证明成功后的荣誉，除了哥德巴赫猜想，还有非常广阔的天地。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下是我对哥德巴赫猜想证明的一些结果\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e满足\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/search?q=%E5%93%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%B4%E8%B5%AB%E7%8C%9C%E6%83%B3\u0026amp;source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_extra=%7B%22sourceType%22%3A%22answer%22%2C%22sourceId%22%3A561454475%7D\" class=\"internal\"\u003e哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/a\u003e的素数对的配对数 大致为\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Gd_%7Bx%7D%3D%5Cprod_%7Bp_%7Bl%7D%2Fx%7Dx%281-1%2Fp_%7Bl%7D%29%281-2%2Fp%29%2B%5Csum_%7Bp%3D3%7D%5E%7B%5Csqrt%7Bx%7D%7D%5Csum_%7Bl%3D1%7D%5E%7Bq-1%7D%27%5Csum_%7Bt%3D1%7D%5E%7Bf%7D%5Cmu_%7Bq%7D%5Cmu_%7Bt%7D%7Bh%2Fq%28%28%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D%28x%2Cq%2Cl%29-%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D%28x%29%2F%5Cvarphi%28q%29%29%7D\" alt=\"Gd_{x}=\\prod_{p_{l}/x}x(1-1/p_{l})(1-2/p)+\\sum_{p=3}^{\\sqrt{x}}\\sum_{l=1}^{q-1}'\\sum_{t=1}^{f}\\mu_{q}\\mu_{t}{h/q((\\pi_{t}(x,q,l)-\\pi_{t}(x)/\\varphi(q))}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上式中\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eq为素数p以及素数p的乘积\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep不整除于x\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=hx%5Cequiv+l%28modq%29\" alt=\"hx\\equiv l(modq)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Csum%E2%80%98\" alt=\"\\sum‘\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 表示对q的缩系求和\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D\" alt=\"\\pi_{t}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e (x)表示小于x的t个素数的积\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ef为小于x 的n个素数乘积的最大的n值\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可以看到后面那一项是比较复杂的，而这一项我本来以为很简单，但是就有一个逻辑漏洞感觉处理不掉，然后苦苦思索了一年多，才发现一个看似初等的问题，实际上就是一个解析数论即等差数列中的素数定理的问题，而要解决这个问题，证明第二项是一个相对小的数，我还需要继续探索。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说明一下曾经让我困惑的那个看起来很初等的问题是\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于一个整数X和两个素数p,q\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如何判定X=np+mq这个式子成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e并不是X越大，就一定成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e例如12=5+7\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是比12大的13就没有相应的式子成立，思索这个问题，我思索了一年，才发现必须转换为解析数论问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总之，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1要估计问题的困难性\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2，敢于探索值得肯定\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3，不要只关注这个问题，如果对数学感兴趣，你完全可以接着自学大学数学课程，发现广阔天地，然后找到真正属于你的领域。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559608484,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c08812a703566bc55861ddaa7fb73752","url_token":"theoneaboveall","name":"TheOneAboveAll","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/b4ec24aff7c30da3521ebd4b7578a7d7_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/b4ec24aff7c30da3521ebd4b7578a7d7_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c08812a703566bc55861ddaa7fb73752","user_type":"people","headline":" 普通的人生总不见得为临时起意的问题学完这一专业吧","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559608484","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545743839,"updated_time":1545885961,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e在看到错误证明前，我觉得话不能说死。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“初等数学证明不了哥德巴赫猜想”也只是个猜想，没人证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e万一数学家的直觉真的错了呢？历史上著名科学家犯错也不少。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上两句话，我想了下这也只是我的猜想，可能不严谨，所以先提问求证一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307132012\" class=\"internal\"\u003e为何哥德巴赫猜想不能用初等数学证明？\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e玻尔，爱因斯坦，泡利等人都作过不少错误预测。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网上说证明出什么猜想，虽然很有可能是错的，但在找出错误前说什么都没有意义。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是我觉得，如果真的发生了这种事，一个不被看好的高中生找到了众多数学家忽视的角度，证明了世纪难题，那人类确实有点可笑。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559541786,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7eb1fd144c72b41a5ae5b9a2077b459e","url_token":"su-ling-8","name":"苏灵","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6ec693522_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6ec693522_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7eb1fd144c72b41a5ae5b9a2077b459e","user_type":"people","headline":"任何学科都可与数学联姻，却不一定能生出漂亮的娃。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559541786","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545737452,"updated_time":1546068000,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e民科的所有证明都只是在玩语言游戏而枉顾其真实意义。这一点，之前那位某伟老师示范得很到位。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许是中二期总会有些想要被别人认可，却不知道怎么办的时候吧。再有就是初中高中这一段时间里做了太多那种抓破脑壳都想不出题目，却可以用奇特的辅助线或者什么其他奇技淫巧就变得非常简单。于是觉得哥德巴赫猜想这种世界难题也是存在一个让人大附中跌眼镜的简便解法吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些数学难题之所以重要不是因为它难度高，而是因为很可能现有的数学工具根本没有办法把这道题解开。换言之能解开这道题，就你发展新的数学工具，从而打开了新世界的大门。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你只是找到了哥德巴赫猜想的反例，却没有足够价值的思路或数学工具，那就和中彩票一样，出一次大名而已。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=380\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=340\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
